Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請使用龍牙槍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:01.05,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(800,1000)}Dragon Tooth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西…像溝口先生那樣做就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 有模有樣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從1200單位距離開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放出目標
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎮定下來 配合呼吸的節奏哦 小姑娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次打中之後再拉遠200單位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命中率維持在90%以上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前距離 2800單位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見前輩真的好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你的眼光挺準啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實戰的情況還不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這孩子挺有天分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好鍛煉鍛煉 讓她單人狙擊也不在話下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為Alivs頭號狙擊手的潛力簡直是滿分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這機體我開不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神劍型的駕駛員擁有特殊的因子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,適合他們的機體是憑此決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是這部Mk.Sein
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一騎的同步率已經高到無法接納他人的協同代碼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎真好命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的機體要是也能給這麼改造一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去求求新聯合國唄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們幫你改造好了 再一下子搶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差點用這傢伙把遠見給同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這機體裡裝了三倍的芬里爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為的就是能炸得一乾二淨 什麼也不留下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種機體 你們也不會想開的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是個未知數 不應該投入實戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士你害怕把她加入系統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一騎和真矢都陷入危險了 你會先救誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒去看真矢訓練嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得在今天之內把這份文件處理好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「島民在俗稱盂蘭盆會或盂蘭盆節的節日中的行動概要」…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說白了就是盂蘭盆祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這時候了還祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為是這時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個島是為了保護「和平」這種文化而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈妹妹 你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見前輩可帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁司令也說能夠馬上上戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠馬上上戰場…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把資料發給你 你幫我向各部門確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 為什麼還需要駕駛員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者在各地活化了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這地方也不知道什麼時候會被大舉進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我當然知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 今天一定要把那事辦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢又出了這檔子事 我家都亂成一鍋粥了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一想到真矢要駕駛法芙娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 明明大家也都是強裝鎮定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正害怕的是孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果大人表現出不安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會給孩子們造成不必要的壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也挺頑強的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了之前那個島的資料和他的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到了延續駕駛員生命的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們未來的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這說明你和你的女兒都具備出色的洞察彼岸的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所做的努力 一定會有回報的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你沒事吧 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好多溝口先生轉來轉去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你來得正好 過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為協同代碼的影響 醉成爛泥了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醉成爛泥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家沒醉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是新手激昂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.22,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(746,1000)}beginner's high
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計是因為第一次訓練緊張壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 接下來就交給你了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她將來可是你重要的戰友 好好把人家送回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰友…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到一騎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠 遠見！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 總士 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 總士和乙姬 你們還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 快救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我正忙著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就負起責任來送遠見回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我這個戰鬥指揮官的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 乙姬 回頭見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士你真是不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那個問題的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論面臨怎樣的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都要保護齊格飛系統內的所有駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你並不是一個人在承受 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好吧 遠見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在應該能自己走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 感覺好像飄飄然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:09:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次下來的時候 走路也是東倒西歪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概是太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高興？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了和大家一樣的景色的那種喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子的心情肯定也是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種感覺 與其說是駕駛法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說是成為了法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是變成了另一個自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會改變的 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我說你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 你怎麼提著這麼多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慶祝你訓練歸來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎要不要也一起來？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天爸爸會回來 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 叫上真壁司令也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢 我去聯繫看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 姐姐你要幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別問了別問了 在媽媽回來之前快做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼說嘛 你就當是幫我個忙唄？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎手藝不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他沒有媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你反正做菜特別糟糕 不如跟他一塊兒住？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我又不是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話媽媽也會承認我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能嘛 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些派出去當主力 然後來個側面攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了！敵人來得比預料的還快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候就要乾脆利落地出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎您回來 媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這是做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說一騎在這兒叨擾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你經常來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 只是偶爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你在想什麼啊 弓子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別裝啦 明明就自己也偷著樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽就只有在真壁叔叔面前會示弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餐具洗好了 還有其他命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 要不要來杯茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 來 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不給我命令的話 我會很為難 不知道該做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就儘管為難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我唯一的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個高難度的任務…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得準備給爸爸過去世後的第一次盂蘭盆節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡量多殺敵 這樣才能告慰爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不會逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天弓子真是太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去這麼多年 我又回想起了建造這個島的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我這麼說很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有人想在島上開始新的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道生和弓子都是值得信任的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還請你支持孩子們的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺這頓晚飯真夠重大的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是覺得有些事情是一直不會變的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也要跳盂蘭盆會舞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建起高台 大家一起跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還會有各種攤點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是舞會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點不一樣吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是祭奠死者的節日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安魂彌撒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 類似這種
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得幫藏前和翔子準備一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 那甲洋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢 蠢材 甲洋還活著吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我沒救成的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再一起去看望他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起跟他說話的話 他肯定會醒的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡不行 不能去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門發出應答 Ambivalent 類型無法斷定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標…未被識別成敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂 防禦幕牆啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓所有駕駛員登上法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門不認為是敵人…難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要真是這樣 那可就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能會有駕駛員遇害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各機配置到各個方位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓Mk.Ⅶ攜帶上次的裝備待在中央
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓遠見…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要足夠的兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能會遭受和摩爾多瓦同等的破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓這種事發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想在我的島上胡做非為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五個方位遭到同時進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各機前往指定地點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時應戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已到達指定位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 高帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太突然了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就看著吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒問題吧 真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會接通音頻通訊 便於你把握戰況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你要聽從我的指示射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人正在同化重力波防護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布倫希爾德系統啟動了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經開始自主防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是那個類型的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下來了？是被打倒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了個少見的種類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可得小心點 卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各機使用配備的火器應戰 千萬別靠近敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙…沒有攻過來？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃癸斯護盾解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅴ 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅷ 在同化行動中消滅牠！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了！幹掉牠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛！所有人瞄準頭部的眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽的 太不搭調了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊給我去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9點鐘方向 1點鐘方向 6點鐘方向的敵人均已消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3點鐘方向的敵人撤向空中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要漏掉一隻 島就會被吃光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒子彈了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅲ 快住手！撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人接觸到Mk.Ⅲ了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有機體都前去支援！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我 媽媽！媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把駕駛員彈出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在做！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這讓我怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我連咲良一起打嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們到達現場了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄準敵人停止動作的瞬間 卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你別動手 壞人我來當
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不是這個島的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們想殺咲良嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凍結Mk.Ⅷ的裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良！咲良！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}救我！救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你寧願我們所有人都被同化嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管他們 卡農！快打！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹嘛鎖住我的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我解鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是動手 敵人就會衝著你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎 我們會把敵人從Mk.Ⅲ身邊引開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後怎麼做交給你處理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引開？要怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點Mk.Ⅶ會處理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說遠見…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者被消滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員全員平安無事！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見前輩…真的太厲害了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部機體撤回向島船塢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家去迎接駕駛員們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕…好害怕啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎你回來 卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…現在才後怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去吃飯吧 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能別對我直呼其名了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是你哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和這沒關係 總士就是總士
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因祭典而喧囂的龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.71,0:23:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭奠的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永不磨滅的音容笑貌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 蒼穹的法芙娜 第二十回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.76,0:23:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈火 -浮燈-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裡嗎
